---
title: Beef-Pork Rissoles & Cheesy Bacon Potato Wedges with Caramelised Onion & Apple Slaw
description: Cheese and caramelised onion together is a legendary pairing in our books, except we’re driving a wedge between them and splitting them up. The gooey cheese is melted over golden wedges and the caramelised onion is served on top of beef and pork rissoles. Even apart they make a perfect match.
